name: Exploding Effigy
description: When Blood Effigy expires it explodes dealing 500~900% of your ability power and stunning for 3 seconds.

name: Blood Ritual
description: Reduces the blood cost of your abilities by 2~30%. After using an ability, take damage equal to 10% of your maximum Health.

name: Bloody Strikes
description: 2~22% chance on hit to Bleed target, dealing 10~35% of your Hero Damage stat as magical damage every second for 5 seconds. Bleeding enemies take 5~15% more damage.

name: Stunning Surprise
description: At the end of cloaked, stun all nearby enemies for 1~3 seconds.

name: Enhanced Effigy
description: Increases the damage of Blood Effigy by 4~40%

name: Effigy Overdrive
description: Increases the damage of Blood Effigy by 3~21% but reduces the lifespan by 10~6 seconds.

name: Exsanguination
description: Gain 1~6 blood upon defeating an enemy.

name: Hunter's Instinct
description: Gain an 4~20% chance to Dodge an incoming attack, taking 0 damage.

name: Lasting Siphon
description: Increases the duration of Blood Siphon by 1~5 seconds.

name: Poison Siphon
description: Blood Siphon is replaced with Poison Siphon dealing 20~500% of your ability power as magical Poison Damage over 5 seconds.

name: Sharpened Stake
description: Increases the damage of Wooden Stake by 4~40%

name: Surging Siphon
description: Increases the damage of Blood Siphon by 4~40%.

name: Tri-Stake
description: The Hunter now throws 2 additional Wooden Stakes but reduces the damage of Wooden stakes by 70~50%.

name: Wound
description: Wooden Stake causes the target to bleed, dealing 20~40% of your Ability Power stat as magical damage. Wound enemies take 5~13% more damage.

name: Ghastly Blades
description: Enemies attacked by Spectral Knights move at 90~60% speed while taking 10~20% extra magical damage for 1~3.5 seconds.

name: World Tree Mcbufferson
description: The World Tree's hero buff now lingers for an additional 2-7 seconds after leaving its radius, and it also increases Hero Damage and Ability Power by 10%.

name: Mass Destruction
description: Increases the Defense Power of the affected tower by 2-70% .

name: Vicious Strikes
description: Increases the Defense Range of the affected tower by 175-2275 units.

name: Radiant Critical Power
description: Increases the Defense Critical Damage of nearby defenses by 0-5% and Defense Critical Chance of nearby defenses by 3%.

name: Explosive Shielding Guard
description: When the affected tower takes damage, it has a 3-35% chance to gain a shield for 50-250% of its Defense Health for 5 seconds and to trigger an explosion that deals 140-500% of its Defense Health as damage to nearby enemies. Does not work with Auras and Traps. This does not destroy the tower. Does not stack with Shielding Guard or Explosive Guard.

name: Thunderstruck
description: Your primary attacks have a 2-26% chance on hit to drench enemies for 3-7 seconds and your primary attacks deal an additional 16-40% damage as storm damage. Storm damage has a 3 second cooldown.

name: Destructive Pylon
description: Increases the Defense Power of nearby defenses to 102-138% and increases the Defense Power of the affected tower by 2-34%. Does not stack with Destruction or Power Pylon.

name: Automation
description: Each time your defense attacks, it heals for 2% of its max health. Cooldown of 0.7 seconds.

name: Juggernaut
description: Increases the Defense Health of the affected tower by 2-70% and increases damage resistance by 2-20%.

name: Genie King's Blessing
description: Gain 1-3 mana upon defeating an enemy, up to 100 enemies per Combat Phase.

source.difficulty: Mastery, 880 Stars and all Chaos 9 Primes

name: Tandem Strike
description: After damaging an enemy, all Defenses deal 5-25% more damage to that enemy for 5 seconds.

source.difficulty: Mastery, 975 Stars and all Chaos 10 Primes
